561
00:36:21.495 --> 00:36:24.392
[SIGHS] After that...

562
00:36:24.416 --> 00:36:26.418
you'll never have to see me again.

563
00:36:27.794 --> 00:36:29.796
Or Yan Mi. I'm guessing. right?

564
00:36:32.090 --> 00:36:33.425
Why now?

565
00:36:36.303 --> 00:36:38.346
Look. you want my help or not?

566
00:36:47.565 --> 00:36:49.025
They arrested her.

567
00:36:51.194 --> 00:36:52.403
No.

568
00:36:53.905 --> 00:36:55.591
They'll deport her
if they don't get the plates.

569
00:36:55.615 --> 00:36:57.626
And even if they do...

570
00:36:58.242 --> 00:36:59.779
Yung Jun will have her diced.

571
00:36:59.803 --> 00:37:01.417
I wouldn't blame him.

572
00:37:02.027 --> 00:37:05.766
This is bad for everyone. including me.

573
00:37:05.791 --> 00:37:07.426
This won't touch you. Chao.

574
00:37:07.451 --> 00:37:09.002
- Oh.
- You have my word.

575
00:37:13.300 --> 00:37:15.010
Look at that.

576
00:37:16.804 --> 00:37:18.722
Itchy onion cut a deal.

577
00:37:19.848 --> 00:37:20.891
Huh.

578
00:37:22.351 --> 00:37:24.228
[SIGHS]

579
00:37:26.230 --> 00:37:28.541
Just stay clear of the ice
factory tomorrow morning.

580
00:37:28.565 --> 00:37:29.794
Hmm.

581
00:37:29.818 --> 00:37:30.961
It will be crawling with cops.

582
00:37:30.985 --> 00:37:34.823
You really think she's worth
blowing all this up?

583
00:37:38.660 --> 00:37:39.953
Yeah.

584
00:37:41.190 --> 00:37:42.524
She is.

585
00:37:47.001 --> 00:37:48.646
[SNIFFLES]

586
00:37:48.670 --> 00:37:51.148
If you're late. I'm keeping this. hmm?

587
00:37:51.172 --> 00:37:52.567
I won't be.

588
00:37:52.591 --> 00:37:53.649
Yeah.

589
00:37:53.673 --> 00:37:59.991
♪ ♪

590
00:38:00.015 --> 00:38:02.184
- And. Chao...
- Just save it.

591
00:38:04.145 --> 00:38:05.413
I'll see you tomorrow.

592
00:38:05.437 --> 00:38:12.444
♪ ♪

593
00:38:16.032 --> 00:38:18.743
[DOOR CLICKS OPEN AND SHUT]

594
00:38:20.370 --> 00:38:22.080
There you are.

595
00:38:24.820 --> 00:38:26.488
Ooh. what's that?

596
00:38:28.879 --> 00:38:30.671
Homemade baijiu.

597
00:38:31.089 --> 00:38:34.092
Father Jun liked to break
it out on special occasions.

598
00:38:35.579 --> 00:38:37.247
I figure this counts.

599
00:38:38.055 --> 00:38:39.056
Yeah.

600
00:38:40.933 --> 00:38:43.311
[BOTH GRUNT SOFTLY]

601
00:38:47.565 --> 00:38:48.959
How you holding up?

602
00:38:48.983 --> 00:38:50.339
I don't know.

603
00:38:51.068 --> 00:38:55.214
I always thought
when this day came. I'd feel...

604
00:38:55.573 --> 00:38:57.260
lost.

605
00:38:57.284 --> 00:39:01.181
But somehow. wherever he is.

606
00:39:01.205 --> 00:39:03.391
I kind of feel like the old man's

607
00:39:03.415 --> 00:39:06.210
prouder of me now than he ever was.

608
00:39:07.461 --> 00:39:09.171
Does that sound crazy?

609
00:39:10.518 --> 00:39:11.954
- No.
- A little.

610
00:39:12.299 --> 00:39:16.136
[LAUGHTER]

611
00:39:19.098 --> 00:39:20.758
By the way...

612
00:39:21.518 --> 00:39:23.579
Hong has a boyfriend.

613
00:39:23.603 --> 00:39:25.522
No shit?

614
00:39:26.434 --> 00:39:29.037
Well. not anymore.

615
00:39:29.108 --> 00:39:30.252
What the fuck are you talking about?

616
00:39:30.616 --> 00:39:32.216
What happened?

617
00:39:33.863 --> 00:39:35.424
I...[CHUCKLES]

618
00:39:36.032 --> 00:39:38.594
Brought my work home with me.

619
00:39:38.618 --> 00:39:40.679
- Oh.
- Well. fuck him. then.

620
00:39:40.703 --> 00:39:41.765
Yeah.

621
00:39:41.789 --> 00:39:43.207
We've got each other. right?

622
00:39:44.333 --> 00:39:46.144
What more do we need?

623
00:39:46.168 --> 00:39:47.378
Damn straight.

624
00:39:48.737 --> 00:39:49.898
Brothers.

625
00:39:49.922 --> 00:39:52.275
♪ ♪

626
00:39:52.299 --> 00:39:53.985
Always.

627
00:39:54.009 --> 00:39:55.403
Always.

628
00:39:55.427 --> 00:39:58.824
♪ ♪

629
00:39:58.848 --> 00:40:00.236
Mm.

630
00:40:00.260 --> 00:40:07.524
♪ ♪

631
00:40:09.401 --> 00:40:10.777
Hey. Chao.

632
00:40:13.155 --> 00:40:16.801
Isaac... what is this?

633
00:40:16.825 --> 00:40:19.011
I don't know how you got off that train.

634
00:40:19.035 --> 00:40:21.347
but you fucked up coming back here.

635
00:40:21.371 --> 00:40:23.331
And I know you killed Happy Jack.

636
00:40:24.416 --> 00:40:26.711
Sound like you got a promotion. hmm?

637
00:40:27.483 --> 00:40:28.939
Right.

638
00:40:28.963 --> 00:40:30.149
I'm the boss now.

639
00:40:30.173 --> 00:40:32.484
And if I don't avenge his death.

640
00:40:32.508 --> 00:40:34.194
I'll have every gang on the coast

641
00:40:34.218 --> 00:40:37.823
thinking I'm weak.
gunning for my business.

642
00:40:37.847 --> 00:40:39.533
And I can't have that.

643
00:40:39.557 --> 00:40:41.160
Wait. wait.

644
00:40:41.184 --> 00:40:42.560
[GROWLS]

645
00:40:44.103 --> 00:40:46.331
I'm worth more to you alive. hmm?

646
00:40:46.355 --> 00:40:47.959
We make deal.

647
00:40:47.983 --> 00:40:49.377
You don't have anything I want.

648
00:40:49.401 --> 00:40:50.986
The counterfeit money. huh?

649
00:40:52.029 --> 00:40:54.448
I know where the Hop Wei make.

650
00:40:55.491 --> 00:40:57.844
I can't attack a Tong in the
middle of fucking Chinatown.

651
00:40:57.868 --> 00:40:58.869
No need.

652
00:41:00.204 --> 00:41:01.765
They're moving plates tomorrow.

653
00:41:01.789 --> 00:41:03.582
Just a few men. hmm?

654
00:41:05.083 --> 00:41:06.762
You can take...

655
00:41:07.878 --> 00:41:11.817
if you know where to be.

656
00:41:11.841 --> 00:41:16.447
♪ ♪

657
00:41:16.471 --> 00:41:18.804
I'm listening. Chinaman.

658
00:41:19.390 --> 00:41:20.951
So talk.

659
00:41:20.975 --> 00:41:27.982
♪ ♪

660
00:41:32.446 --> 00:41:34.740
[DOOR CLATTERS OPEN]

661
00:41:36.242 --> 00:41:38.887
[FOOTSTEPS TAPPING]

662
00:41:38.911 --> 00:41:40.412
[DOOR BANGS SHUT]

663
00:41:46.961 --> 00:41:48.764
Evening. lads.

664
00:41:49.255 --> 00:41:51.650
I take it you all work
for Mr. Strickland.

665
00:41:51.674 --> 00:41:52.968
That's right.

666
00:41:55.929 --> 00:41:57.156
And those are for me?

667
00:41:57.180 --> 00:41:59.683
Mr. Strickland said to make it hurt.

668
00:42:03.103 --> 00:42:04.890
You mind if I finish my beer first?

669
00:42:09.484 --> 00:42:12.463
[TENSE MUSIC]

670
00:42:12.487 --> 00:42:19.120
♪ ♪

671
00:42:21.622 --> 00:42:23.100
[GUNSHOT]

672
00:42:23.124 --> 00:42:26.294
[ALL YELLING AND GRUNTING]

673
00:42:27.712 --> 00:42:29.106
[GUNSHOT]

674
00:42:29.130 --> 00:42:35.636
♪ ♪

675
00:42:53.489 --> 00:42:56.366
[GROANING]

676
00:43:04.250 --> 00:43:05.895
No. no. no. no.

677
00:43:05.919 --> 00:43:07.605
No. no. no. No. no.

678
00:43:07.629 --> 00:43:09.398
- [BONES CRACK]
- [SCREAMS]

679
00:43:09.422 --> 00:43:12.485
[GRUNTING]

680
00:43:12.509 --> 00:43:19.516
♪ ♪

681
00:43:32.363 --> 00:43:34.257
[GROANING]

682
00:43:34.281 --> 00:43:36.367
[SHOUTS]

683
00:43:39.203 --> 00:43:40.704
[YELLS]

684
00:43:42.290 --> 00:43:44.769
[YELLS]

685
00:43:44.793 --> 00:43:46.687
[BLADE SWISHES]

686
00:43:46.711 --> 00:43:49.690
[RAPPING IN A CHINESE LANGUAGE]

687
00:43:49.714 --> 00:43:56.721
♪ ♪
